    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading1"><text styleclass="Heading1" translate="true">Polynomial 2-3 Motion-Law</text></para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Heading3 Underline_atocs_"></para>
    <para styleclass="Heading3 Underline_atocs_" style="page-break-before:always;"><text styleclass="Heading3 Underline_atocs_" translate="true">Polynomial 2-3 Cam-Law, Motion-Law</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text"><table styleclass="Default" rowcount="2" colcount="1">
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Heading4 Toggle_atocs_"><text styleclass="Interface2" translate="true">Motion Description</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><table styleclass="Block" rowcount="1" colcount="1">
            <tr style="vertical-align:top">
              <td>
                <para styleclass="Body Text"><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true">A </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MT-Motion-Cam-Laws" anchor="Standard" styleclass="Body Text" translate="true">Traditional Motion-Law</link><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true">. &#160;Its name is often reduced to Parabolic Velocity, or Poly 23.</text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">45.</text></para>
                <para styleclass="Body Text"><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true">A motion with continuous </text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">Velocity</text><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true">, from start to end. </text></para>
                <para styleclass="Body Text"><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true">There are large </text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">Acceleration-Discontinuities</text><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true">, with infinite jerk, at its start and end.</text></para>
                <para styleclass="Body Text"><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true">It gives a low peak velocity, but a high peak Acceleration. </text></para>
                <para styleclass="Body Text"><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true">It has a low Jerk value at the </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MT-Cross-Over" styleclass="Body Text" translate="true">crossover</link><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true"> point (the mid-point).</text></para>
                <para styleclass="Body Text"><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true">Its Torque characteristic is very good.</text></para>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </table></para>
          <para styleclass="Heading4 Toggle_atocs_"><text styleclass="Interface2" translate="true">Motion-Values</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true">Use the Control-Buttons and the Flexible Polynomial motion-law</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><table styleclass="Block" rowcount="1" colcount="1">
            <tr style="vertical-align:top">
              <td>
                <para styleclass="Parameter"><image src="MT-CamLaw-Polynomial23-BPE.ipp" imagestyleclass="Default" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"><caption translate="true"><![CDATA[Flexible-Polynomial Control-Buttons for POLYNOMIAL 2-3]]></caption></image></para>
                <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#343400;" /></para>
                <para styleclass="Parameter"><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true">Edit the </text><text styleclass="Parameter" translate="true">Start Position</text></para>
                <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true">The </text><text styleclass="Parameter" translate="true">Start-Position</text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true"> usually </text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">flows</text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true"> from the </text><text styleclass="Parameter" translate="true">End-Position</text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true"> of the </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MT-Previous-Segment" styleclass="Element" translate="true">Previous-Segment</link><text styleclass="Element" translate="true">.</text></para>
                <para styleclass="Bullets"><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true">Edit the </text><text styleclass="Parameter" translate="true">End Position</text><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true">&#32;</text></para>
                <para styleclass="Bullets"><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true">Use the Control-Buttons to force the </text><text styleclass="Parameter" translate="true">Start-Velocity</text><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true"> and </text><text styleclass="Parameter" translate="true">End-Velocity</text><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true"> to Zero (units/s)</text></para>
                <para styleclass="Bullets"><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true">Deselect the </text><text styleclass="Parameter" translate="true">Start-Acceleration</text><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true">, </text><text styleclass="Parameter" translate="true">End-Acceleration</text><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true">, </text><text styleclass="Parameter" translate="true">Start-Jerk</text><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true">, and </text><text styleclass="Parameter" translate="true">End-Jerk</text><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true"> Control-Buttons.</text></para>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </table></para>
